Wendy’s/Arby’s Agrees to Sell Arby’s Restaurant to Roark for $430 Million

-- B y   J o A n n e   N o r t o n
-- 
2011-06-13T11:01:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-13/wendy-s-arby-s-agrees-to-sell-arby-s-unit-to-roark-group-for-430-million.html
Wendy’s/Arby’s Group Inc. said it
agreed to sell Arby’s Restaurant Group to a buyer formed by
Roark Capital Group for $430 million. Wendy’s/Arby’s Group will
retain an 18.5 percent ownership interest in the Arby’s
business.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
JoAnne Norton at 
 jnorton@bloomberg.net  